# ====================================================================
# Quick-start: pick the provider that matches where your Excel lives.
# ====================================================================
#
#   Local file (incl. OneDrive sync folder, iCloud, Dropbox):
#       cp .env.example.local .env
#
#   Microsoft 365 (SharePoint / OneDrive for Business sharing link):
#       cp .env.example.m365 .env
#
#   Google Sheets (template only — not yet implemented):
#       cp .env.example.googlesheets .env
#
# Then edit .env to fill in your specific values.
# ====================================================================
